graph TD
    A[I/O Callback] --> B[Poll Phase]
    B --> C[Execute I/O Callback]
    C --> D[process.nextTick Queue]
    C --> E[setImmediate Queue]
    D --> F[Drain nextTick]
    F --> G[Drain Microtasks]
    G --> H[Check Phase]
    H --> I[Execute setImmediate]
    I --> J[Close Callbacks]
    J --> K[Next Tick]
